        "content": "<p>Yes we do, see eg <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=NormedSpace.expSeries_hasSum_exp#doc\">docs#NormedSpace.expSeries_hasSum_exp</a></p>",
